        <p>This letter is to confirm your acceptance to provide locum tenens coverage at {!crRecord.TR1__Account__r.Name}. The assignment set forth herein and payment for professional services rendered are contingent upon your completing the Curative quality assurance process, approval of malpractice coverage, and completion of {!crRecord.TR1__Account__r.Name}’s credentialing process. To ensure proper reporting enrollment under State Patient Compensation Fund rules and regulations, Curative must be notified 24 hours prior to your providing professional services on any dates not listed below.</p>
         
        <p>Curative will be assisting you with your travel and lodging arrangements, if applicable. Under no circumstances is Curative liable to reimburse travel expenses that are not arranged through Curative or approved by {!crRecord.TR1__Account__r.Name}. Personal expenses such as long distance phone calls, meals, gasoline, entertainment, laundry, etc. will be your responsibility.</p>
         
        <p>We ask that you complete paperwork required for clinic and/or hospital privileges in a timely manner to ensure adequate time for processing.</p>
         
        <p>Curative agrees to pay you the following rates for the specific location and dates listed below. If holiday premium rates are applicable, please refer to the holiday call and work clause in your provider services agreement.</p>
         
